To statically compile package hey we need the following:

```
export GO_EXTLINK_ENABLED=0
export CGO_ENABLED=0

go build --ldflags '-extldflags "-static"'
```

otherwise go build will produce dynamically linked executable.
This is due to non-GO implmentation of net/http package used in hey.

